        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This spellheart is fashioned from the tip of a demon\u2019s horn that\u2019s been polished until smooth and shiny. The spell DC of any spell cast by Activating this item is 17. \n* **Armor** You gain resistance 2 to unholy.\n* **Weapon** After you cast an enchantment spell by Activating the horn, your Strikes with the weapon deal an additional 1d4 mental damage until end of your next turn.",
